title: Prehistoric Women 1950 (fantasy adventure film) by Gregg G. Tallas starring Laurette Luez

sources.title: Prehistoric Women 1950 (fantasy adventure film) by Gregg G. Tallas starring Laurette Luez
sources.description:
A civilization of gorgeous cave-women abduct men for mating purposes. One of their victims is Engor, who seems to be smarter than the rest of the men. He discovers fire, battles a monstrous giant and attempts to win the hand of the prehistoric queen.

Original title: Prehistoric Women (1950) 


Director: Gregg G. Tallas
Writers: Sam X. Abarbanel, Gregg G. Tallas 
Stars: Laurette Luez, Allan Nixon, Joan Shawlee
Genres: Cult, Adventure, Fantasy, Psychotronic


00:00 Full Movie (with subtitles)
01:14 A tale of prehistoric women led by Tigri, facing oppression and seeking freedom in a jungle setting.
07:55 Mysterious prehistoric women outsmart and outmaneuver a terrifying jungle monster.
26:30 Engor embarks on a journey to rescue his tribe from captivity and discovers the power of fire.
38:04 A tale of survival and power struggles in a prehistoric tribe led by Tigri and Engor.
1:00:34 Engor and Tigri's marriage ceremony marks the beginning of a new era for their tribes.
